name: Grand theft auto 5
author: Hulevych
description: When a young street hustler, a retired bank robber, and a terrifying psychopath find themselves entangled with some of the most frightening and deranged elements of the criminal underworld, the U.S. government, and the entertainment industry, they must pull off a series of dangerous heists to survive in a ruthless city in which they can trust no one—least of all each other.

name: Call of duty 4
author: Hulevych
description:
The rules of engagement have been rewritten. From the shadows of Chernobyl to the heat of the Middle East, you are the silent professional standing between order and global collapse.

Join the SAS and US Marines in a gripping race against a rogue ultranationalist threat. In this war, there are no front lines—only the mission. Check your corners, watch your six, and trust your squad.
